		<p>Thank you for visiting www.trepic.co (the “Site”), which is owned and operated by Trepic, Inc., a Delaware corporation (“Trepic,” “us,” “our,” or “we”). Trepic takes privacy and transparency very seriously. Please read the following privacy policy (the “Policy”) to understand how your Personal Information will be collected and treated as you make full use of the Site as well as all related applications, software, and services (together, and collectively with the Site, the “Service”). For purposes of this Policy, “Personal Information” means information that can or potentially can be used on its own or with other information to de-anonymize data or to identify, contact, or locate a single person.</p>

		<h3>1. SERVICE ELIGIBILITY</h3>

		<p>Our intent is to collect personally identifiable information only from individuals who are at least 18 years old, who are legal residents of the United States with a legitimate email and mailing address, and who voluntarily provide such information by completing the registration process to participate in the Service. If you fail to meet any of the criteria described above, you may not complete the registration process or any forms on the Site or available through the Service that request Personal Information.</p>

